{"tid":991600,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【新聞背後】一旦引渡美國 孟晚舟最高面臨30年監禁","createTime":"2019-01-22T13:15:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-23T01:20:40.000Z","uid":141151,"like":54,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"d1dcaa2784b06de1d8cc1ed62e3d834b80364622","tid":991600,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T13:15:48.000Z","msg":"【新聞背後】一旦引渡美國 孟晚舟最高面臨30年監禁<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E3%80%90%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%E8%83%8C%E5%BE%8C%E3%80%91%E4%B8%80%E6%97%A6%E5%BC%95%E6%B8%A1%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B-%E5%AD%9F%E6%99%9A%E8%88%9F%E6%9C%80%E9%AB%98%E9%9D%A2%E8%87%A830%E5%B9%B4%E7%9B%A3-035723435.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%25E8%2583%258C%25E5%25BE%258C%25E3%2580%2591%25E4%25B8%2580%25E6%2597%25A6%25E5%25BC%2595%25E6%25B8%25A1%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%259C%258B-%25E5%25AD%259F%25E6%2599%259A%25E8%2588%259F%25E6%259C%2580%25E9%25AB%2598%25E9%259D%25A2%25E8%2587%25A830%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E7%259B%25A3-035723435.html&d=AqY7y7jJ%2FuWEOQGpCgMhp0kviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=5d0f610d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E3%80%90%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%E8%83%8C%E5%BE%8C%E3%80%91%E4%B8%80%E6%97%A6%E5%BC%95%E6%B8%A1%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B-%E5%AD%9F%E6%99%9A%E8%88%9F%E6%9C%80%E9%AB%98%E9%9D%A2%E8%87%A830%E5%B9%B4%E7%9B%A3-035723435.html</a><br />\n<br />\n中國華為太子女、副董事長兼首席財務官孟晚舟上月初在加拿大轉機，加方應美國要求將其拘留。由於孟晚舟涉嫌違涉嫌誤導金融機構和違反美國對伊朗制裁禁令，有關指控最高可判處30年監禁。<br />\n<br />\n由於孟晚舟向加拿大法院申請「禁止報道令」，法庭不可披露美國指控。檢方表示，孟晚舟於2009至2014年，透過香港空殼公司Skycom與伊朗交易；當時作為Skycom首席財務官的孟晚舟涉嫌誤導金融機構，令對方與Skycom續有生意往來。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，孟晚舟一旦被引渡美國，將會面臨合謀欺詐多家金融機構的指控，每項指控最高可判30年監禁。孟晚舟亦被指違反美國對伊朗制裁禁令，違規向伊朗出售美國商品，違例者最高可被罰款100萬美元（約780萬港元）及監禁20年。"},{"pid":"cbbc6cd963c7977a01f005bb3590219c6c1458dd","tid":991600,"uid":64374,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T13:31:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b83f47ccfe85a11925d9c496dad3fd1c61596436","tid":991600,"uid":211579,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T13:33:32.000Z","msg":"得罪美國仲要得罪埋以色列<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"416a87b83c8203824fb94ed55786ee1c408827af","tid":991600,"uid":61280,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T13:37:09.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">坐完支那仲有冇共產黨呢？？？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"c338f43d7cd450eb67654e0f1d9f1e38b1dd1eaa","tid":991600,"uid":65956,"like":36,"dislike":0,"score":36,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T13:37:29.000Z","msg":"能夠餘生都喺美國渡過，應該係好多支国人嘅畢生夢想<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbf39f3edeb201242f9763166e06326d2631dd15","tid":991600,"uid":8171,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"416a87b83c8203824fb94ed55786ee1c408827af","tid":991600,"uid":61280,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T13:37:09.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">坐完支那仲有冇共產黨呢？？？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong></span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T13:43:20.000Z","msg":"坐完仲有冇命都成問題"},{"pid":"0b52fe3b54d950ff57fc5abcda1cbd9ba0e9c54d","tid":991600,"uid":14494,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"dbf39f3edeb201242f9763166e06326d2631dd15","tid":991600,"uid":8171,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"416a87b83c8203824fb94ed55786ee1c408827af","tid":991600,"uid":61280,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T13:37:09.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">坐完支那仲有冇共產黨呢？？？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong></